		<title>09Religion and Beliefs</title>
		<content>                                       
                                       
 Bridford Mills Gospel Hall - two      
 services, Communion and Evening with a
 congregation of 20.  Once a month a   
 general service - congregation 30.    
                                       
 All churches have other informal      
 meetings eg prayer meeting, bell      
 ringing, women's meeting, Mother's    
 Union.                                
                                       
 The Church of England have absorbed   
 within their congregation members of  
 the Methodist and Presbyterian        
 Churches.  The Roman Catholics in the 
 area use the Ashton Church of         
 England church building for worship.  
                                       
                                       
                                       
